Installation
============

1) Create Makefile
$ perl Makefile.PL

2) make and install
$ make
# make install

3) Set up necessary data in database
# make initdb

4) Activate the plugin in RT
Add the following line to your RT_SiteConfig.pm:
Plugin( "RTx::Action::SubjectAndEvent" );

5) Restart your RT's httpd, e.g.:
# /etc/init.d/httpd restart
